dmca.title: NetEnforcers complains of Panamax images in Froogle
dmca.body:
Attn: Legal, DMCA complaints

I, the undersigned, CERTIFY UNDER PENALTY OF PERJURY that I am an agent
authorized to act on behalf of the owner of certain intellectual property
rights, said owner being named [Panamax] ("IP Owner"). I have a good faith
belief that the listings or materials listed below are not authorized by the
above IP Owner, its agent, or the law and therefore infringe the IP Owner's
rights according to state, federal, or United States law. Please act
expeditiously to remove or disable access to the material or items claimed
to be infringing.

Identity of advertisement(s) at issue/Images owned by [Panamax]/:

Beach Audio http://froogle.google.com/froogle_image?q=http://beta.beach audio.com/products/m5100-ex.jpg&dhm2fe4439c

I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification
is accurate and that, for each image identified above, I either own the
 
copyright or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive
right that is allegedly infringed.

Truthfully,
/S/: [private](Original Signature on File)
